Description: New sister company launched from Polhill Communications to act as a strategic communications and management consultancy for the financial services sector.

Will offer a range of marketing, communications and management consultancy services and tailored products including:

market entry strategy, positioning and business development planning; 
business consultancy, especially in relation to the formation, operation and development of sales forces and the IFA market; 
marketing and communications audits (both internal and external); 
market overviews and competitor analysis; 
the provision of on-site overspill or crisis management support, with individuals or teams; 
innovative training in interview techniques for executives, including those operating in culturally different/difficult areas of the world; 
specialist environmental consultancy on meeting the challenges and expectations of climate change and using it to enhance your brand 
one-on-one director level consultancy/ mentoring/ leadership training;

Description: Prunelle est une agence de conseil en communication nutrition, spécialisée dans le conseil et la communication en nutrition :

Spécialistes des stratégies nutrition, nous mettons à votre disposition sept atouts décisifs pour construire et gérer le positionnement nutritionnel qui va renforcer votre image de Marque : 

1. notre aptitude à concevoir des plateformes stratégiques et des messages cibles séduisants (plaisir, émotion, surprise, humour, ludisme…) sur la base de données scientifiques souvent austères ; 

2. notre œil critique pour l’audit nutritionnel des gammes existantes ou à développer ; 

3. notre créativité pour construire des modes de communication média et hors média adaptés à vos cibles et à vos objectifs ; 
4. notre parti pris de favoriser ou de mettre à profit vos interfaces internes (juridique, R&D, marketing, commercial, nutrition...) ;

5. notre fonction de veille sur les stratégies nutrition des différents intervenants agro-alimentaires ou pharmaceutiques et des instances gouvernementales et réglementaires à l’échelon européen et nord Américain ;

6. notre culture et notre pratique du travail en réseau, avec d’autres agences, y compris les vôtres ;

7. notre maîtrise des campagnes internationales, autrement dit nos compétences pour décliner vos campagnes nutrition.

References: Kiri, Knorr, Miko, Findus, Milka, Taillefine, Auchan...

TBWA World Health France, pôle santé de TBWA France, a signé un accord de partenariat commercial avec Prunelle, agence indépendante de conseil et de communication spécialisée en nutrition dirigée par Isabelle Rigaud et Patricia Boulos.

Description: In a crowded marketplace where companies compete for the same customers, it’s become hard to stand out. Consumer definitions of value and loyalty are changing. Marketers therefore look to loyalty management providers to help them define and execute a customer loyalty strategy that overcomes these obstacles to build profitable relationships with their best customers. Enter Aimia. We understand customer loyalty better than anyone because we built our business around it: We grew from a single frequent-flyer program into a global leader in loyalty management offering a full suite of services including Coalition Loyalty, Proprietary Loyalty and as Loyalty Analytics.

Our unique capabilities include proven expertise in building proprietary loyalty strategies, launching and managing coalition loyalty programs, creating value through loyalty analytics and driving innovation in the emerging digital and mobile spaces. We are a recognized leader in customer loyalty. Aimia deploys the full suite of loyalty management services on behalf of our clients in order to:

Increase market share in environments of competitive parity;

Increase share of customer via shifting spend from the competition and increasing spend via cross-sell and up-sell initiatives;

Improve lifetime customer value by identifying and overcoming sources of attrition;

Enhance the customer experience in order to create loyalty and brand advocacy.

We deploy our full suite of loyalty services across all industries, geographies and channels. Through our coalition loyalty programs, we share long-term trusted relationships with millions of consumers around the world. We build and run loyalty programs for ourselves and for some of the world’s best brands. Customer data is at the heart of everything we do.
